                <mxCell id="leg" value="&lt;b&gt;V3 Normalization Changes (V2 → V3)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;color:#b85450&#39;&gt;REMOVED (redundant):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• user_handles: current_rating, max_rating, rank_title → user_platform_stats&lt;br/&gt;• user_solves: difficulty_tier → derived from problems.difficulty_tier_id&lt;br/&gt;• submissions: problem_name → derived from problems.name&lt;br/&gt;• solutions: inline AI fields → solution_analysis only&lt;br/&gt;• contest_history: old_rating, new_rating, rating_change → rating_history&lt;br/&gt;• user_stats: week_1..4_solved, easy/medium/hard/expert_solved,&lt;br/&gt;  solved_800..2500+ flat columns → user_tier_stats table&lt;br/&gt;• leaderboard_cache: total/weekly/monthly_solved → user_stats&lt;br/&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;color:#82b366&#39;&gt;NEW tables:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• problem_editorials (1:1) — tutorial_url, tutorial_content,&lt;br/&gt;  tutorial_extracted_at, tutorial_solutions extracted from problems&lt;br/&gt;• user_tier_stats — replaces flat solved_XXX bracket columns&lt;br/&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;color:#9673a6&#39;&gt;MERGED:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• sync_checkpoints → sync_jobs&lt;br/&gt;  (fixed VARCHAR platform → platform_id FK,&lt;br/&gt;   added last_checkpoint_at)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Notation:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;PK = Primary Key  FK = Foreign Key&lt;br/&gt;UK = Unique Key  NN = Not Null&lt;br/&gt;Solid line = mandatory FK&lt;br/&gt;Dashed line = optional FK (SET NULL)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#666666;fillColor=#f5f5f5;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=10;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=6;" parent="1" vertex="1">
